  {"id":"lg7_d734","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Could you hold this for me?","ja":"これを取り置きしてもらえますか？"},
  {"id":"lg7_c700","type":"comprehension","level":"B1","text":"Thank you for your purchase. You have thirty days to return any item with the original receipt for a full refund.","question":"返金の条件は?","choices":["30日以内かつ元のレシート","無条件","14日以内","交換のみ"],"answer":"30日以内かつ元のレシート","ja":"30日以内・元レシートで全額返金。"},
  {"id":"lg7_c701","type":"comprehension","level":"B1","text":"Your account balance is low. To avoid an overdraft fee, please deposit funds before any pending payments clear.","question":"手数料を避けるには?","choices":["入金する","口座を閉じる","カードを止める","連絡する"],"answer":"入金する","ja":"残高不足。当座貸越手数料を避けるため、引き落とし前に入金を。"},
  {"id":"lg7_c702","type":"comprehension","level":"B2","text":"We received your complaint about the late delivery. As an apology, we're offering a twenty percent discount on your next order.","question":"提供されるのは?","choices":["次回20%割引","全額返金","送料無料の継続","商品交換"],"answer":"次回20%割引","ja":"配送遅延の苦情へのお詫びに次回20%割引。"},
  {"id":"lg7_c703","type":"comprehension","level":"B2","text":"Before approving the loan, the bank will check your credit history and verify your income with recent pay slips.","question":"銀行が確認するのは?","choices":["信用履歴と収入","学歴","住所のみ","家族構成"],"answer":"信用履歴と収入","ja":"融資承認前に信用履歴と給与明細で収入を確認。"},
  {"id":"lg7_c704","type":"comprehension","level":"B2","text":"This jacket is part of our final clearance. All sale items are non-refundable, but you may exchange them within seven days.","question":"セール品の扱いは?","choices":["返金不可だが7日以内交換可","返品自由","交換不可","返金のみ"],"answer":"返金不可だが7日以内交換可","ja":"最終セール。返金不可だが7日以内なら交換可。"}
